AdvancedIllnessDiagnosis</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="5a444f66-7ce5-496e-b1a6-3d046140b925" name="Outpatient Encounters with Advanced Illness" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>( [Encounter: "Outpatient"]
    union [Encounter: "Observation"]
    union [Encounter: "ED"]
    union [Encounter: "Nonacute Inpatient"] ) OutpatientEncounter
    with "Advanced Illness Diagnoses" AdvancedIllnessDiagnosis
    such that exists (
    OutpatientEncounter.diagnosis.condition Condition
    where EndsWith(Condition.reference, AdvancedIllnessDiagnosis.id)
    )
    and OutpatientEncounter.period starts 2 years or less before
    end of "Measurement Period"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="a9410e9d-ca64-446e-9a2e-02b0595fd82e" name="Long Term Care Periods During Measurement Period" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>( [Encounter: "Care Services in Long-Term Residential Facility"]
    union [Encounter: "Nursing Facility Visit"] ) LongTermFacilityEncounter
    where LongTermFacilityEncounter.period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    return LongTermFacilityEncounter.period
    intersect "Measurement Period"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="1ab1bd33-abc3-413e-b337-5cfb2dc32288" name="Inpatient Encounter with Advanced Illness" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>[Encounter: "Acute Inpatient"] InpatientEncounter
    with "Advanced Illness Diagnoses" AdvancedIllnessDiagnosis
    such that exists (
    InpatientEncounter.diagnosis.condition Condition
    where EndsWith(Condition.reference, AdvancedIllnessDiagnosis.id)
    )
    and InpatientEncounter.period starts 2 years or less before
    end of "Measurement Period"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="235b750f-5138-4aca-bec1-c09cb6f3f394" name="Dementia Medications In Year Before or During Measurement Period" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>["MedicationDispense": "Dementia Medications"] DementiaMed
    where DementiaMed.whenHandedOver as dateTime during day of Interval[
    ( start of "Measurement Period" - 1 year ), end of "Measurement Period"
    ]</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="afc58125-af01-46bd-8ca9-2f91f63fa765" name="Has Criteria Indicating Frailty" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>exists ( [DeviceRequest: "Frailty Device"] FrailtyDeviceOrder
    where FrailtyDeviceOrder.authoredOn during day of "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists ( [DeviceUseStatement: "Frailty Device"] FrailtyDeviceUse
    where FrailtyDeviceUse.timing as Period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    or FrailtyDeviceUse.timing as dateTime during day of "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists ( [Condition: "Frailty Diagnosis"] FrailtyDiagnosis
    where FrailtyDiagnosis.onset as Period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    or FrailtyDiagnosis.onset as dateTime during day of "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists ( [Encounter: "Frailty Encounter"] FrailtyEncounter
    where FrailtyEncounter.period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    )
    or exists ( [Observation: "Frailty Symptom"] FrailtySymptomObservation
    where FrailtySymptomObservation.effective as Period overlaps "Measurement Period"
    or FrailtySymptomObservation.effective as dateTime during day of "Measurement Period"
    )</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="f7d5506a-6b64-4e6a-8c83-fa7b36a752eb" name="Advanced Illness and Frailty Exclusion Including Over Age 80" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>(
    Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(FHIRHelpers.ToDate(Patient.birthDate), start of "Measurement Period")in Interval[66, 80]
    and "Has Criteria Indicating Frailty"
    and ( Count("Outpatient Encounters with Advanced Illness")>= 2
    or exists ( "Inpatient Encounter with Advanced Illness" )
    or exists "Dementia Medications In Year Before or During Measurement Period"
    )
    )
    or (
    Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(FHIRHelpers.ToDate(Patient.birthDate), start of "Measurement Period")>= 81
    and "Has Criteria Indicating Frailty"
    )</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="d5b8921a-0d3e-4c2d-a6eb-428253605268" name="Advanced Illness and Frailty Exclusion Including Under Age 80" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(FHIRHelpers.ToDate(Patient.birthDate), start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
    and "Has Criteria Indicating Frailty"
    and ( Count("Outpatient Encounters with Advanced Illness")>= 2
    or exists ( "Inpatient Encounter with Advanced Illness" )
    or exists "Dementia Medications In Year Before or During Measurement Period"
    )</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="6a232850-a030-4185-9505-c6704364f315" name="Has Spent More Than 90 Days in Long Term Care" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"Days Spent in Long Term Care During Measurement Period" > 90</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="b39cd9bb-e1b2-42e3-ba50-53630a54bc26" name="Days Spent in Long Term Care During Measurement Period" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"CumulativeDays"("Long Term Care Periods During Measurement Period")</logic><comment></comment></definition></definitions><functions><function id="5f466572-2310-4463-9c13-a8ec0fbf9c7c" name="CumulativeDays" context="Patient"><logic>Sum((collapse Intervals)CollapsedInterval
    return all duration in days of CollapsedInterval
    )</logic><comment></comment><arguments><argument id="39e658c9-19e2-40b2-a612-8c49005ea299" argumentName="Intervals" type="List<Interval<DateTime>>" qdmDataType="List<Interval<DateTime>>"/></arguments></function></functions><includeLibrarys><includeLibrary id="5f97b3bb-0b2c-4bae-b111-258ddfed34aa" name="FHIRHelpers" cqlLibRefId="FHIRHelpers-4-0-0" cqlLibRefName="FHIRHelpers" cqlVersion="4.0.000" qdmVersion="4.0.0"/><includeLibrary id="12d7dbec-0600-4fa4-85d6-f4aafa440b1c" name="Global" cqlLibRefId="MATGlobalCommonFunctions-FHIR4-4-0-000" cqlLibRefName="MATGlobalCommonFunctions_FHIR4" cqlVersion="4.0.000" qdmVersion="4.0.0"/></includeLibrarys></cqlLookUp>', 0, null, now(), '402803826529d99f0165d450f7d02f61', 'FHIR', '4.0.0');

    [Encounter: "Encounter Inpatient"] DischargeHospice
    where DischargeHospice.status = ''finished''
    and (
    FHIRHelpers.ToConcept(DischargeHospice.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition).codes[0] ~ "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)"
    or FHIRHelpers.ToConcept(DischargeHospice.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition).codes[0] ~ "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)"
    )
    and DischargeHospice.period ends during day of MeasurementPeriod
    )
    or exists (
    [ServiceRequest: "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospiceOrder
    where HospiceOrder.intent = ''order''
    and FHIRHelpers.ToDateTime(HospiceOrder.authoredOn) in day of MeasurementPeriod
    )
    or exists (
    [Procedure: "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospicePerformed
    where HospicePerformed.status = ''completed''
    and Global."Normalize Interval"(HospicePerformed.performed) overlaps MeasurementPeriod
    )</logic><comment></comment><arguments><argument id="0752a76f-51ca-449d-9a71-d485fdff5012" argumentName="MeasurementPeriod" type="Interval<DateTime>" qdmDataType="Interval<DateTime>"/></arguments></function></functions><includeLibrarys><includeLibrary id="0e37ceaf-1a2c-428f-bf03-f4071af9fc7e" name="Global" cqlLibRefId="MATGlobalCommonFunctions-FHIR4-4-0-000" cqlLibRefName="MATGlobalCommonFunctions_FHIR4" cqlVersion="4.0.000" qdmVersion="4.0.0"/><includeLibrary id="6ccb32e5-21e4-46a8-998c-3debcaf4b3b4" name="FHIRHelpers" cqlLibRefId="FHIRHelpers-4-0-0" cqlLibRefName="FHIRHelpers" cqlVersion="4.0.000" qdmVersion="4.0.0"/></includeLibrarys></cqlLookUp>', 0, null, now(), '402803826529d99f0165d450f7d02f61', 'FHIR', '4.0.0');

    else if onset is FHIR.string then

    where P.intent = ''order'')
    union
    (["Procedure": "Comfort Measures"] InterventionPerformed
    where InterventionPerformed.status = ''completed'')</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="3a4e0419-595c-4d7f-8ad6-ecaca1e85386" name="All Stroke Encounter" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"Non Elective Inpatient Encounter" NonElectiveEncounter

    or Global.PrincipalDiagnosis(NonElectiveEncounter).code in "Ischemic Stroke"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="51e102f9-2664-4ed3-865a-9ca8a243eaaf" name="Ischemic Stroke Encounter" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"Encounter with Principal Diagnosis and Age" EncounterWithAge
    where Global.PrincipalDiagnosis(EncounterWithAge).code in "Ischemic Stroke"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="f511d0dc-13ef-42fa-94c7-ca22c11507cc" name="Non Elective Inpatient Encounter" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>["Encounter": "Non-Elective Inpatient Encounter"] NonElectiveEncounter
    where Global."LengthInDays"(NonElectiveEncounter.period) <= 120
    and NonElectiveEncounter.period ends during "Measurement Period"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="32bf6382-d98b-47db-b645-9e8ad0274e72" name="Ischemic Stroke Encounters with Discharge Disposition" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"Ischemic Stroke Encounter" IschemicStrokeEncounter
    where IschemicStrokeEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition in "Discharge To Acute Care Facility"
    or IschemicStrokeEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition in "Left Against Medical Advice"
    or IschemicStrokeEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition in "Patient Expired"
    or IschemicStrokeEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition in "Discharged to Home for Hospice Care"
    or IschemicStrokeEncounter.hospitalization.dischargeDisposition in "Discharged to Health Care Facility for Hospice Care"</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="d49195f4-3c21-4e4b-a5b5-092c4d94a958" name="Comfort Measures during Hospitalization" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"Ischemic Stroke Encounter" IschemicStrokeEncounter

    such that FHIRHelpers.ToDateTime(Coalesce(ComfortMeasure.performed as dateTime,ComfortMeasure.authoredOn)) during Global."HospitalizationWithObservation"(IschemicStrokeEncounter)</logic><comment></comment></definition><definition id="65e1eece-13af-4bf1-bb8f-f870257d1df2" name="Encounter with Principal Diagnosis and Age" context="Patient" supplDataElement="false" popDefinition="false"><logic>"All Stroke Encounter" AllStrokeEncounter
